data.description: *Assumable VA loan,3.25 interest rate on this Lennar home, built 2020, in the Independence planned community. Enjoy the 3 car garage,5 bedroom (1 non conforming) and 3 bath with a partially finished basement.The kitchen is the heart of the home with a large island, plenty of seating, white cabinets, granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, gas range, stainless steel appliances and  sink.The laminate vinyl plank flooring make for easy living with a main floor office with new custom doors and wood blinds.The Pinnacle floor plan allows for an eat in kitchen and spacious family room with designer paint and wood accent wall.The outdoor trek deck,covered patio and concrete extended side patio for barbecuing or gathering around a fire pit creates the perfect outdoor setting.The sellers added turf grass to save on water bills and low maintenance living. Enjoy the meadow view to the right of the property from the yard and walking paths, parks and trails right outside your door.The new community pool opened this summer, fitness center and clubhouse, all included with the district metro tax. Wander upstairs to a spacious master suite with designer paint and wood accents,granite countertops, walk in closet and beautifully tiled shower and flooring.The upstairs is complete with three more bedrooms and bathroom with dual sinks, granite countertops and a spa tub.Don't miss the finished basement with decorative brick wall feature, electric fireplace, extra family room (man cave) non conforming bedroom or office along with  a large workout gym or storage. Why wait for new when you can move in and begin a enjoying your  home with all the landscape and window coverings included. Amenities, grocery, shopping are both accessible in Elizabeth&Parker.The covered front porch,new roof, efficient solar plans from ION are assumable,105.00 monthly)are all included for you this peaceful Independence community location.
